## Logistics Pipeline

```
mock.Generate({{VOLUME}})
→ Reconcile      ERP shipment vs carrier invoice by tracking_number
→ Landed Cost    freight + duties + insurance + customs fees
→ WAC            weighted average cost per SKU, no float
→ Ledger         double-entry entries per reconciliation status
→ Quarantine     carrier invoices without matching ERP (excluded from WAC)
→ Reprocess      reversal + recalculation when invoice is corrected
→ Reports        reconciliation, ledger, risk — CSV + read-only API
```

