## What lives in the source repo

- `internal/domain` — Money, ERPShipment, CarrierInvoice, reconciliation, landed cost, WAC, ledger, reprocessing
- `internal/mock` — deterministic data generator with fixed seed
- `internal/service` — full pipeline orchestration
- `internal/report` — DTOs and mappers
- `internal/export` — CSV export
- `internal/api` — read-only HTTP API (inventory, ledger, risk)
